  Steps to instal tomcat server

 # wget http://www.us.apache.org/dist/tomcat/tomcat-7/v7.0.68/bin/apache-tomcat-7.0.68.tar.gz

 #tar xzf apache-tomcat-7.0.68.tar.gz
 #mv apache-tomcat-7.0.68/usr/local/tomcat7

To Start the services we need to go into the location 

 #cd /usr/local/tomcat7

 the run the following command

#./bin/startup.sh

 After to deploy the project the project *.war file should be downloaded to 
 the following location.

#cd webapps/ 

 To run the project open the browser and enter the url 

 127.0.0.1:8080/name of the project (where 8080 is the default port number of th e apache server)

